WHAT IS NOT INCLUDED IN THIS LICENSE
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The following items are PROPRIETARY to PINGEQUA and are explicitly NOT 
covered by either license above. They are not present in this repository:

  • Specific component selections (regulator part numbers, capacitor 
    values, antenna matching network components)
  • PCB stackup, copper weight, impedance-controlled trace dimensions
  • Manufacturing files (Gerber, drill files, pick-and-place data)
  • Bill of Materials with specific manufacturer / part numbers
  • Proprietary firmware or test fixtures developed for the Hydra RF 
    production line

These remain trade secrets of PINGEQUA. Licensing of any such material 
would be subject to separate negotiation. The open architecture 
documented here is sufficient for educational purposes and DIY builds 
without requiring access to these proprietary details.

